HEADWORD: Beambird
<hw>Beam"bird`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A small European flycatcher (<spn>Muscicapa grisola</spn>), so
called because it often nests on a beam in a building.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

